laboratory_examinations.findings: Consistently undetectable or present at very low concentrations in serum, with only slight increases when serum FT4 concentrations fell below normal levels.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Serum TSH concentrations remained undetectable or very low for several years. After radical treatment, TSH levels increased, reaching the normal range.
